[ctns_make id='func_slope_for_increasing_values_of']

  [ctns_front style='']
Slope $$m = \frac{ \Delta y }{ \Delta x}$$ <br/> For increasing Values of $$y$$
  [/ctns_front]  

  [ctns_back style='width:80%;font-size:90%;']
The slope $$m$$ is Positive for increasing values of $$x$$ and increasing values of $$y$$,  $|m = \frac{ \Delta y }{ \Delta x} \gt 0|$
  [/ctns_back]  

  [ctns_backspeak]
The slope m is Positive for increasing values of x and increasing values of y.
  [/ctns_backspeak]  

[/ctns_make]
